{"type": "article", "id": 18140, "title": "吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-27T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141115I362ilVgh9FmYnKH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t巴塞罗那的设计事务所 Goula/Figuera 做了这组极具艺术感的吊灯，从上千幅绘画手稿中选择了 8 种元素，然后用焊接钢铁的方式完成。一些地方点缀了一些彩色的实心圆点，呼应几何感的线条，既古典又现代。各种元素重叠在一起可以形成一盏大灯，有雕塑的美感，放在小孩的房间也不会显得奇怪。这一系列灯组可以联系定制，<a href=\"http://www.goulafiguera.com/homeadventures/s-h-o-p/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141112YigvHN9Pue5jwJfO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50534188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141113PKEOoGCJyb5QUYpi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50641026\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141113xM3KwBucCAafJWtO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50641026\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141114i9T1hGveLHCg6lAx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50534188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061411146x4beEynjoGwhUWJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.52564103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}